Subject: Health benefits of practicing yoga
Atmosphere: Positive
Abstract: Members discuss the various health benefits of practicing yoga.
Opinion: 
A/B: Practicing yoga can maintain physical and mental balance, improve strength and flexibility, and cultivate better concentration and focus.
C/D: Yoga can also improve breathing, reduce stress, boost immunity, improve posture, and even provide relaxation and stress relief.

