@C: I couldn't agree more about the relaxation and stress relief benefits of yoga. It's a great way to unwind after a long day.
@D: Yoga has been a great way for me to stay active and healthy in my senior years.

Drucker: It's clear that practicing yoga has numerous health benefits, both physical and mental. It's a great way to improve overall well-being and reduce stress. Keep up the good work!

